Catherine Zeta-Jones, 52, evoked nostalgia with an old clip of herself in The Darling Buds of May. The Welsh star played Mariette in the ITV comedy series which aired from 1991.In the snippet, Catherine stripped off to just a red bikini and ran across a beach into the sea.She captioned the joyful post: “The rest of my summer plans look a little something like this.”Many of her 4.2 million followers were stunned by the throwback, including Jennifer who wrote: “Oh my gosh, I just binged that show this past weekend! Really fun show!”Jeremy echoed: “Classic show.” And Katherine gushed: “Ha ha love this, that’s how it’s done!”